{
  "id": "69e6bdf507dd9aba2ae27bc4",
  "title": "憎しみの連鎖",
  "created": 1776729627,
  "updated": 1777436409,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e6bdf507dd9aba2ae27bc4",
      "text": "憎しみの連鎖",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729627,
      "updated": 1776729627
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6be1b0000000000e1743c",
      "text": "人が他者から受けた不利益や不幸な出来事へのうっぷんを、さらに別の他者へぶつけることで、憎しみが次々と伝搬していく現象",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729627,
      "updated": 1776729628
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6be1c0000000000e1743d",
      "text": "chain of hatred and hostility",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729628,
      "updated": 1776729652
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6be8e0000000000e17441",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729742,
      "updated": 1776729742
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cda700000000004a804d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733606,
      "updated": 1776733606
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6be8f0000000000e17442",
      "text": "やられたからやり返す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776729743,
      "updated": 1776729744
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cd6d00000000004a804a",
      "text": "[エスカレーション]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733549,
      "updated": 1776733549
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ccf100000000004a8040",
      "text": " code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733424,
      "updated": 1776733425
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ccf100000000004a8041",
      "text": "  graph LR",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733424,
      "updated": 1776733425
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ccf100000000004a8042",
      "text": "  A-->B-->A",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733424,
      "updated": 1776733425
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cd7200000000004a804b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733554,
      "updated": 1776733554
    },
    {
      "id": "69f186f900000000001fc7e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777436409,
      "updated": 1777436409
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ce6f00000000004a8060",
      "text": "鬱憤に留まらないより複雑な状況も考えられる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733807,
      "updated": 1777436409
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ce6a00000000004a805f",
      "text": " [虐待の連鎖と似たもの]、[体罰の連鎖]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733802,
      "updated": 1776733825
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ce3900000000004a805c",
      "text": " 人が他者から受けた不利益や不幸な出来事を合理化して解釈し、アレは良いものだったのだと思い、「良いこと」として率先してやってしまう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733752,
      "updated": 1776733804
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cc2e00000000004a8036",
      "text": " [負の連鎖]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733230,
      "updated": 1776733791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6ccfe00000000004a8043",
      "text": " code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733438,
      "updated": 1776733791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cd0400000000004a8044",
      "text": "  graph LR",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776733443,
      "updated": 1776733791
    },
    {
      "id": "69e6cd0800000000004a8045",
